{"tid":820420,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有打丁先定有扑野先","createTime":"2018-09-15T11:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T13:19:02.000Z","uid":134958,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"febf8783ed0237971dc7e5a6761df0663fba3fcb","tid":820420,"uid":134958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"而家討論嘅範圍唔係人類 係人類進化樹上嘅物種 (至少要有丁,西)<br />\n打丁：不論手打 定物件<br />\n扑野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得有打丁先 <br />\n因為扑野點都要集合兩個不同性別,再不斷磨合<br />\n但係打丁就只要劣吓劣吓就會發現 <br />\n何況天然環境上都好多天然洞,無咩可能咁多洞入面第一個試嘅就係西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37e303afe030c89b9f1d697cb589f94a643637a","tid":820420,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"靚仔 扑野<br />\n毒撚 打丁"},{"pid":"3fdf94f6d9d263ed37e051823d5bc50f893fbbbe","tid":820420,"uid":134958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b37e303afe030c89b9f1d697cb589f94a643637a","tid":820420,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"靚仔 扑野<br />\n毒撚 打丁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:59:42.000Z","msg":"已經係格硬嚟嘅時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚咪不要暗戀&hellip;&hellip;囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d30c4733fa9740193f171c832b1889e428e292c","tid":820420,"uid":56618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:00:49.000Z","msg":"應該係扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繁殖下一代係生物本能<br />\n然後有d唔夠強既無機會留低個dna<br />\n唯有打丁發洩"},{"pid":"6406bd9bd6066e58819ef239d05b349ed669b50d","tid":820420,"uid":208440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"如果冇人扑野比你睇你又點打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565418e10a106a5689abc1c918942aa34c8ba815","tid":820420,"uid":175523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:19:02.000Z","msg":"無扑嘢撚有撚打"}]}